text: Christian Brunner (born 2 April 1953) is a former Swiss cyclist. He competed in the 1000m time trial and team pursuit events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Switzerland Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
